OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,FITV News Granada Reports journalist
OL,7,FSam Taylor went along to a track day
OL,8,Fto see how Speed of Sight is changing
OL,9,Flives.
OL,11,FA group of blind and disabled people
OL,12,Fhave praised a "life changing"
OL,13,Fexperience that gives them the chance
OL,14,Fto drive their very own race cars.
OL,16,FWigan-based charity Speed of Sight
OL,17,Fuses special vehicles designed to
OL,18,Fensure anyone can get behind the wheel
OL,19,Fand take on sharp turns at high speeds.
