OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,FThe cars come with dual controls and
OL,7,Fspecial kit to enable a safe driving
OL,8,Fexperience, regardless of any
OL,9,Fdisabilities the driver might have.
OL,11,FJohn Galloway co-founded Speed of
OL,12,FSight in 2012 out of a desire to make
OL,13,Fsure everyone gets the chance to drive.
OL,15,FHe said: "No matter what their
OL,16,Fdisability may be - they could be
OL,17,Fblind, cerebral palsy, down syndrome,
OL,18,Fautism or people who have strokes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
