OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,F"When they come to these track days
OL,7,Fthey'll have a drive that the world
OL,8,Fhas told them is impossible."
OL,10,FNetty Sanderson suffered a stroke in
OL,11,F2018 and had to give up her licence,
OL,12,Fbut at the track day at the Three
OL,13,FSisters Race Course she was given the
OL,14,Fchance to get behind the wheel for the
OL,15,Ffirst time in seven years.
OL,17,FShe said: "I can't put it into words.
OL,18,FIt's absolutely amazing. I just feel
OL,19,Fme again.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
