OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,F"I had a stroke and it took all of my
OL,7,Fleft-sided vision, and so I've not
OL,8,Fbeen able to drive a car since. It's
OL,9,Ftaken my independence and everything
OL,10,Felse - but today I just feel like me."
OL,12,FDrivers like Netty drive
OL,13,Findependently, with an instructor next
OL,14,Fto them with their own set of controls
OL,15,Fwho can keep them safe and provide
OL,16,Fguidance.
OL,18,FNetty said: "These guys are just
OL,19,Famazing. Really enthusiastic and
OL,20,Fsupportive... Just brilliant."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
