OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,FWhile Speed of Sight mainly provides
OL,7,Fthose who will never be able to drive
OL,8,Findependently the chance to get behind
OL,9,Fthe wheel, they recently saw their
OL,10,Ffirst participant take what he's
OL,11,Flearned onto the roads.
OL,13,FHarvey Goodinson is a regular at the
OL,14,FSpeed of Sight trackdays. Born with a
OL,15,Frare condition called segmental spinal
OL,16,Fdysgenesis, the 19-year-old was told
OL,17,Fhe would never be able to drive.
OL,19,FBut everything changed when he first
OL,20,Fgot involved with Speed of Sight at
OL,21,Fthe age of 11.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
