OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,FHe said: "I first started coming in
OL,7,FYear 8. My mum found it online, and I
OL,8,Fkept coming back because I really
OL,9,Fenjoyed it.
OL,11,F"It was fun to drive on a track."
OL,13,FEight years later, Harvey has done
OL,14,Fsomething he was told would be
OL,15,Fimpossible. In April 2025 he passed
OL,16,Fhis driving test with his own
OL,17,Fspecially adapted cars based off of
OL,18,Fthe ones used by Speed of Sight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
