OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,FHe said: "They've been life changing
OL,7,Ffor myself. They've made it possible
OL,8,Ffor me to drive - I met my driving
OL,9,Finstructor through these events - It's
OL,10,Fmade a lot of things possible."
OL,12,FHarvey was taught to drive by Andrew
OL,13,FBevan, a full time driving instructor
OL,14,Fwho volunteers at Speed of Sight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
