OL,3,C'Today I feel like me': Blind and
OL,4,Cdisabled people given chance to drive
OL,6,FWhile it was a lot to learn for
OL,7,FHarvey, it was also a first for Andrew
OL,8,Fwho had never taught a disabled person
OL,9,Fto drive.
OL,11,FHe said: "It was a challenge.
OL,12,FEverybody's used to your standard
OL,13,Fsteering wheel and three pedals but
OL,14,FHarvey's is different.
OL,16,F"He has to do everything different. He
OL,17,Fhas to do everything with his hands,
OL,18,Fso we had to come up with a new system
OL,19,Ffor Harvey that suited Harvey - and
OL,20,Fonce we'd got that combination of hand
OL,21,Fcontrols and routine it just worked."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
